据报道，数十名也门在美国对胡塞叛军的袭击中被杀。）特朗普的国家情报主管塔尔西·加巴德（Tulsi Gabbard） &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=a768105efb424190aac58e97d4a548e4&amp;amp;_e=0LEYqD3fmMhMkvQPr4679nFncvQ8sTUgLrDqsQ5vT7LNPksn72f_-abEnfJ1c2DXX1VwBfdFdKULbT7mqhhZun0pCWub8tWU3dElMvSd9drKF8MxoNTeqeyC7rrunEx1kBLIKVVhKaoEK-eYCkd781SFfhBlf9q7HW1hX0yTKnujR102mgMVgT0lmuC1yqcBG8V2Af7TYtDfGgiGtq3RN9YB_eBC-1E1L-Q6vtN4-6OdJu2NcJrdkOMJkJZyMtSK8Lbh53HMxkenav7FIgIlNcjb57ll9TnHelnqeZMYuXtn-v4YJhxwIZaSH68faxs0n19pAQV14nHIXvJkVChpST8MJ8letqU1HKdTEiMO6EuMzGqCKMDuzc4yHmjI6FVIH9zIMGDdoF6h4vJvT1AuhuPniKrpF0KT0TleySJezdNW5y376uoGUdbMx_PFmJBqC5wOjMH9uPckgLMWZQgSNw-xCyWP1TFhHaetXwjAtRq_VfhXZ1GB-KkI_XAY9xvA_e3LwgnYIZj71RGagcX9vTRVh23tiwqPtFy2hMiSjOvB4KL1aZt5btn6V-LFoz4DlAG2vuAX8uJ2ov278jGwoTH1qngvbzWKPxSISVCByh1nKWLp5jFlUiqRXeLoEnUg" target="_blank"&gt;也在聊天&lt;/a&gt;。尽管共和党对参议院的控制权，她和赫格斯都面临着艰难的提名听证会，因为他们缺乏当前角色的传统经验。赫格斯（Hegseth）是前国民警卫队步兵官员，周末有线电视主持人，尽管现在有了公开的成绩单，但仍讨论了战争计划。现年44岁的赫格斯周三表示：“没有人发短信计划。” “你知道谁看到了战争计划？我看到了他们。”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/UMb9LSOx5OrT-I9hW277YSItH5Nf43Z8HkkSEADmcM9tvpL9keQpzJyk0PobryyRcMkZLBo3FdBgQaRCUiuCMaG8cSpEnJjLhibhQ-Wmnf5KU0bP5RIqYfwC6uYbNU8I6-TdqrGzpKN1c8y28MZGheM5i5r9sV58QF2KXidVmfmXdEjZqS-twVPf0X0sHk98T0cYm7nb5veEWimzFn7V9AjowIfPBo0vmTcrP6nUJZGOng7TYJMf9BbXk8abgSVOD_cCWchzkRv6f6NZvvU491gGY4Gnar-pTwDoeZf8pxBY5MMurpkn6kq3I2JCHX91Cm-4X6r-yAVNN9tIStubVPZkzgji3ULyFmXukgqYmxv3qcqBqhsp3RsJXjsBL6CT0j3kjpdrYwho2idvE6ChOk3rxs2JjPtxVeJmtTM1_YCO444Rx9_aiCofrW4nRp-Z7p77egetQG8GwMQl3eqqIQerERoXG_U5ZjrCcpmCK0JzXP-UVNOo1DOkzyO0U7mdR9RzgXxFuiMA6lZ-48HgK5is94T4QxMqUZ7s6XQHDuQrfGZ6yWuwuKQ3HDjoa_9skVzs6T9b5EpqTbczPkJbQ6EOT8_3/aqnU0qKBUM0_aFf6kR5w4x4cKClI9GnU/7" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iRMpiygpoGWU/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&