li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;由于埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）的特斯拉公司&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/fdsMtvczLT25NcwOfSg4fLmI73TCfyT87xJvuZScQcWgq95NNSW7X62GQEx16rDmbhq8s2eJOvFLl9DYslUzL8AdBO48-GQ2qW4rYiGVbuOBjyvPCfAdqz5Ihkg8xBXkbF93GAQ_tMlFzh1DS9pDaUelgB0rKGmJqMuGhZcHWgH_ZJZRlXEtyW5ZKLOn8X7z0D_1LRxwkCnH4VJAX7E34lVgNkTONqtVzieMyI1V5eblgpoQopdO_FLF0f7i-7mLeZEvbcSuFIyQGbC8l0kkNt_k0R4OiHRaqbOa_orqmAZPCU5b3UwJEcjD8MWbiA5snoWwQ_FqzoyCm1gA_fgGEel3hxuRj6elh6thsXq00aBIZu-Uhnv7fOHqt9Y/6KiO0V7XA1HRtnDSU6lJt__dsRQSvs5o/7" target="_blank"&gt;（&lt;/a&gt; Tesla Inc.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;摩根大通公司（JPMorgan Chase＆Co。）的资产管理部门是&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/yDRxI0KeJB1qyTZ16AETU_NpFVn0Le0jigsCASEZsBc-8EfE_RSlQL21kc7kaBbZlx_OhqlE32a5IDM9MrEgwmqq3bwIm4RQcMZeL7xBUOdLU-60drJYJ_-9zKGEzhzWDwhvqbT03X9tjK01A74nodDkjeTyA7JpHczTbICE3CKiR-kiz9_LKNjANyLREOx2jTE2yqxMEXgOtbYubqTtxMJ0kyL6kXyZg9Atc1SjQctzYEKTLmkxauzyFTe3cFX2oZZ8DqywwkvF7MLL7sVaZLqJCq0ST8MkXzcONz0z13-ACNPtRV5PPDOyXmCeJfNAU_Z8KthDt7gx9dThw0aUgJNMhj-4B-cYFJkhNqGaf5NQLzpr_jo9nXmf56w/8ZQWyov1c-h4ntJB1oJbu9Ry5lFo0lu5/7" target="_blank"&gt;最新的华尔街商店，该商店逃离了&lt;/a&gt;右侧的压力，逃离了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/xCcPbi9caYF8t82cx1fuMP-Qi_S0_fR24CKRxpEMqKlFFC-4WsOHUtnhgFGO5zL5OYGrEpA0WYEJYQ5reCYocvaOHleOQelFEvoxv74DOMqIwakgJAdsHhSFNPPSNCJl0AJR9ODeTPkvokawsCbcafIk3yoDc0FF0tD97hiSOu5PnB3QfOoRAIF31GUqYVq9YQwe8eTVskW4d1JiJqgd0jwxXd1VqwdXtrzfwjZZQrU9xOe-X7c7_y1SmqHTzKilyMysIm98H0ARr-QDgQhj7yTGrCm0BAdNzC3S57EhDuS4sqNDZDM5ecwZwscaErb3FLMwzqg1bLY6RC6c8Oh2JPrT5R6NDsMMBrBibEkwT7_jTyBZRu6rHRmKxaA1WIYbCJypXaZKPhcC_1snA1RWFsGuRbwnhrX_QWww1DTt8oEt6YzaXEtvAHQJ_RNTFOXf1Qo/rZk_oG5OPIrrrXY5Ow7O7UHN01OZYPwV/7" target="_blank" title="链接到网站"&gt;净零资产经理倡议&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;来自绿色的更多信息&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;联合国&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/KxuAD4YChVBsg3R441L4P06P2-Mz7QlFhuWbBKYDPKjDGj-sxJfv5lvP_WwOMbGQsJl-fzLCjApnszVCX-puuiOd19vaqhbjl1qpxUB-WHXKPQ9ERF9YGUyrLgKdhVAq_jSboJcs6Q0JyYISBXuvoMRUcQ1eBuEP2Mta6mlSP0uOdZt1yJfEqYQ_UxfHSoI4dL9ZCMx4Z98VluH-Msus6RRoJtwaZ2cXj7u6I-ZnOsuB0JujSS-2LcHckaTVdTozh8lOAKd6Fo0QZBe4Zaem0KXsrZNyUncaXO7JzE4E0-kF2Ab2igGfEkT_j_5tpPjirYMyG049rjew7BzcaJp2pojmrtuPCuVZL19RbkzrMqGnNU-wYjypcayaohg/5nlau5ptBE7nYGOGaHH7gjWGG_wrHa_o/7" target="_blank"&gt;加大了对欧盟提出其延迟气候计划的压力&lt;/a&gt;，以填补美国留下的外交真空。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;联合国气候机构执行秘书西蒙·斯蒂尔（Simon Stiell）表示，欧盟必须通过提出其减少排放计划，以表现出“领导力”。它将于上个月到期，必须在11月在巴西举行的COP30峰会之前提交。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;全球地缘政治转变使打击气候变化的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/7shzMvYMc-ylgVBoLNiiPNPfc03SQUwzs16DkiWYDSx8Wfvi3bSVfaFr3PnBYbrR0VWhWV9Yof82zq7hv-gEM3LYz0GVFHyQPiYZDawJ3aMJc6o2udq0bc0Cn7izTeukLGAWtN-OucyknRrYZmgTwBp2aCjdfpGczj_Px00VOyiIpXb0Ugc1yBwcadg-LixAjKRIrcrjQ8_motWxvlftv3IaZQ9y_U2cWjVgtKFTY5Sh_h3Y-RyJKmDx3cTBb3vgIBy10iq8lzy_fc-MbaO5mhFFYiAcuKgV7zDVjEpp5XMBsp24ofHuGw62jn8F0MGN4hiND02AQ9qORoftSJzGwh4bsH1p3d8izPNzxl0jaoZ_bM4GenhIZpw6P28/4kEgY-AKrAVFUxn9XBDHNilB6lFoHvBN/7" target="_blank"&gt;斗争变得复杂&lt;/a&gt;。美国退出《地标巴黎协定》的撤离可能会削减发展中国家的资金，而其不愿支持欧洲国防的支持将挤压欧盟预算，从而有可能将资源从绿色过渡中转移出来。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;斯蒂尔在柏林的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/230m4q-dIDnGsqGMQJMdrQPdw9zvV3ltMmkVrEAfHabCpyLaF9be5gxmGLbCQp0rpbLl1q8xa10UW38vnkhhzD_FgykO7NANQh3dTA8G9ET-0RTci5P0k8plLGDgWsIGTadDJIDegqTvlnRbls9jHMpewDSFleQbm61K8e0IYBcGJjjuK6Z0ZP28QUtK8GyNKJG7au1Jgmm-dLVl8Y7g_EYyVFhigUl6gSJLKO7Rq47MVAwzK5fOiVPbXJgclrlk4OujV5HxrnR8EOwE9mC1TYKJd5UT-VxgLFogdBFZoHn-AaoMZJZHWCERRo_kWav_uuRwRrR8ShThIiIgDHZ3dQFXkx_TSVqzH1QhLfE9arEwNMrUDAb30gE0b_Q/qbhvg-ZQ8kOGC1ivJRjEOozhppK0QVqb/7" target="_blank"&gt;演讲中说&lt;/