ily: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;新研究发现甲烷排放量不足&lt;/strong&gt;。联合国委托进行的分析表明，澳大利亚嘉能可（Glencore）的Hail Creek煤矿发出的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/IA3lSqGDAwp-T2MjIK8qf7Cy2COaPeef_oaqs8PaJFAx38gI4pXxRMa2rmsnz2I1eN6OJ0biU4-cjLUfn3-KgvWPJcQa6scTv2desLoSH1mbAMXWPI4CVejwQVSde5HIcrPs9zS2D2w4cjSK232aE9RGuM3n87DSqQio89uvc1_88PJcxv1uxdELW47qsuwNL-ALoCFMw-7MbygQF1iRieDV4cBn5mXY7T-CgDlAHhPyIN2xCD_h0iuf039Fo-NoY-rZWSU1KQs0Mye2COvn0kD7J1diB1qTngrmXn7EMuieYxc8dyWqEVmBAb60CILFHcNK384b6vCl3YfgGAtlQuhrXEUSPuWC7nlmR1pfBfq-UyoeLO1nVAdKs3A/GOm9fVKuVK_QsAP3dI2E_Jeiy9L1lor0/7" target="_blank"&gt;甲烷比报告的三倍至八倍&lt;/a&gt;，质疑是测量温室气体的常规方法的准确性。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;西班牙风暴的天气带有一线希望&lt;/strong&gt;。该国最近的暴风雨&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/XjyDjKa3vFlyN9JYAFcjFNun5oPZCw0vtGCK4Ucxmu_5PoS_XRi4TLJR7ewQ7FEPhRgsqsmP2tlLcV87kPSWYf1Oqibdw2RbSx_hKp81MyZXigY1MlVFyrakEfPLmpfvU_9QeHIEHIFR3VE4-tjME23G2j8pQSA4eSv85Ei62nDccfVI0v73IoVBUy3saK8u1klu-5VSWI4Lyapc7FkERPquBFwIUOc36FRIo9_6ow2grhRqXcRbaov1qrBgjH10C338cIt_zHBhf2SI463rVPZj6aZtjQa-56vUQ-H_-vh39Y4X5qSDFzJE2eQP-T_u6Eztacq8oOzkTG2U17tWXJSnN-CYK-TV_4diztyJaJAnT_cS8uUkoL0TDbM/RGgPNKIda-tkEw8fF2_2gmaTz7FKqwMu/7" target="_blank"&gt;可能终止了该国记录的历史上最严重的干旱&lt;/a&gt;，而三月前三周的降雨量增加了三倍。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;有关更多的天气见解，请直接发送到您的收件箱， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/iAELUyLxUUK5gGs8PAjidbbT4nzIDTqYLJ2f1JN1qjYbwPuyKDQoorlSI9MBsyPRsoyk5IqZPcxaWfIRKUawVotasRzamid76uv8UsXyHoXYZQlDnokNS18yIfXSLTqBJBJwdQxb4aUTVxVWGFDbYwkDCIDo-6rISnPo33YJGHAiD2KwiJWuqvYy1ASR9nPUEmQgsEs3Dr5-I3wRpgTrWhpqKo7j50KZw8tgnCuVji5SeQDgHwka5OhIC8t3s6BBgbj0mxzv9UcaAxTPtMkCxuuoVsQyyjAujgWQacKNSuMe4nSSGVRtDIL2ghrd3ocx1jv2_8b5xmQH503hqPgdkX55lhiiY7SddihVy57BMBehUuAXcNjVQDWAECc/b--USGtAOPryrK56Ur6J6n6U2G5yon-O/7" target="_blank"&gt;请注册&lt;/a&gt;Weather Watch新闻通讯。&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;现在流媒体&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;科学家正在开发越来越强大的磁铁，以实现融合等清洁能源。但是中国在稀土磁铁中供应链的主导地位威胁着他们的全球可用性。寻找一种新型磁铁是六部分跨行星系列&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Ua-lxMUloX5rkOnabss1Up6OEVSKiBVZTH_0QpoebH6vSEMo-gctCJldJGhRLmDKKMv-QqOSiJ8_wcbU0cZyTDXHWl1G-myVBPj5wb2Sdlq7a9kK4I4jIfYS6NhCe0YV97eVRdMkhr9h6Ru5k_pzM7quSpn4WB9NjPMtNA_XkgU-cn3236QI34jIBTAlW-iN9aq9Q5i93-2X1vOI4zQFnffK-fDPt_FoHrGt132FSoZleCA5azdevswAbDNMjZoUb_lT3UYiL2X9jqJcbV7xT0XsQcy_62Xu8eb_lGHDYil-1U6aEiVk87hXeT6SrMtau_rAyTOO5VJP3u_ZxgF1mceU_6lGij9SOTU5NB7usMrB9Rlj2q33hVhk5PI/-hR473pghgN6-PRsgggNYxzdC_bhzlxC/7" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;em&gt;彭博底漆&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;中第一集的重点，该系列彭博底漆着眼于塑造我们未来的“不可能”行业。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/uOOVA39b13BCCir0KaHPi5Ao5ngTnb6sHgujOMCPWHt-w51MvmDJERazFdWlKPdJ_U9NXJlpI42MERS0tEexj573Y_f4JlKgNwIq2D-uJUJJ8QRt0x4Zk2uWFuMjUL9hGdVQ15aWcgqCFnv_az-v-3DUDSE8nJrmEssRBQfIn3Oq9sgiw_w5m3yya4Ti-uRt-hDm1NNSWjgXztVRwhmEgLMbFzrBfzIU8BaxKYHLXu6cteXsA9gW9OCIGfN5YkGhO1K16ymPYuk63Ryg48V4hPvLxS01nGzi0XPGCASZgVpLgc88fSu4D86q9z-4O-NYHDe4iZfJxoAGmK4PY-UBQ0ExbBYa2-ECBZA9Puo19ll0tIrvkJAkDKjJUig39XX1z9TBgivflyNMtMUNUOoPZqU9-HphelHlBdD1IS2kJKnErrSp9amaeAuAwE-nZziZcrXJgw/7FUrjfbdqWivzeZt-DeX3iH_1oH1rQSN/7" target="_blank"&gt;在此处&lt;/a&gt;观看彭博原版的完整剧集。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/yrI0_lCS76wuVw76LMov-B3nj-yTx0zkBCvBHY7WmiiZyHP3Gf4BKDInT5jT4xebN6Ph00U5njySWM8ViHJf8BdMxdmVfFS0TCwHLiz2arDcqL3r6hKbvxXcZlUIo9qx9xzCkqS7AO0BXT8yYnlMH6MeBNnNHGPe67CGxJx2qAgoNTuKBPQzAESSE7-8VJWl9cU8aqDVV_JNBIVrV9Yd9hre_38sQAzHbJFA5XTdgq5ZZICS3-F_qDjy-SDmqVgnZMepG3rnYL29rfVXBJKKZ5JmKNkLgssZ62FTg4GN6LDz_bKzaymUQfxnbxOLKn1tPRMUyXMCv_Cgv-OdngHAVLU5VivyfQN_dv7